note left of ServicePy
    **trip_service.py** (~600 lines)
    
    Core Business Logic:
    
    Class: TripService
    
    Main Methods:
    - plan_trip() → routes to fast mode
    - plan_trip_fast() → 1 AI call
    - plan_trip_agent() → unused
    
    Helper Methods:
    - _format_response()
    - _format_weather_summary()
    - _format_pois_list()
    - _generate_weather_summary()
    
    Fast Mode Flow:
    1. Calculate metrics
    2. Get coordinates (OSM)
    3. Get weather (Open-Meteo)
    4. Get POIs (Overpass)
    5. Single LLM call (Groq)
    6. Parse & validate JSON
    7. Format response
    
    Performance:
    - Response time: 5-10 seconds
    - LLM calls: 1 (vs 5-8)
    - Cost: ~$0.001/request
    - Success rate: 99%+
end note

